{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.1","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:1","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Menaces de l\u2019\u00c9ternel contre Isra\u00ebl et Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. Ps 50:1-4. (Os 8:1-6; 13:16. 2 R 18:9-12.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut adress\u00e9e \u00e0 Mich\u00e9e, de Mor\u00e9scheth, au temps de Jotham, d\u2019Achaz, d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias, rois de Juda, proph\u00e9tie sur Samarie et J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.4.11","name":"Jonas 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.2","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:2","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\u00c9coutez, vous tous, peuples!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sois attentive, terre, et ce qui est en toi!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, soit t\u00e9moin contre vous,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le Seigneur qui est dans le palais de sa saintet\u00e9!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.3","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:3","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Car voici, l\u2019\u00c9ternel sort de sa demeure,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il descend, il marche sur les hauteurs de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.4","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:4","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>\n    Sous lui les montagnes se fondent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Les vall\u00e9es s\u2019entr\u2019ouvrent,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme la cire devant le feu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme l\u2019eau qui coule sur une pente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.5","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:5","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et tout cela \u00e0 cause du crime de Jacob,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A cause des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quel est le crime de Jacob? N\u2019est-ce pas Samarie?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quels sont les hauts lieux de Juda? N\u2019est-ce pas J\u00e9rusalem?\u2026<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.6","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:6","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Je ferai de Samarie un monceau de pierres dans les champs,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Un lieu pour planter de la vigne;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je pr\u00e9cipiterai ses pierres dans la vall\u00e9e,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je mettrai \u00e0 nu ses fondements.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.7","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:7","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Toutes ses images taill\u00e9es seront bris\u00e9es,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tous ses salaires impurs seront br\u00fbl\u00e9s au feu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je ravagerai toutes ses idoles:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Recueillies avec le salaire de la prostitution,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles deviendront un salaire de prostitution\u2026<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.8","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:8","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-16: cf. \u00c9s 36:1, 2; 10:28, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi je pleurerai, je me lamenterai,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je marcherai d\u00e9chauss\u00e9 et nu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je pousserai des cris comme le chacal,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et des g\u00e9missements comme l\u2019autruche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.9","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:9","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Car sa plaie est douloureuse;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle s\u2019\u00e9tend jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Juda,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elle p\u00e9n\u00e8tre jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la porte de mon peuple,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Jusqu\u2019\u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.10","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:10","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>\n    Ne l\u2019annoncez point dans Gath,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ne pleurez point dans Acco!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Je me roule dans la poussi\u00e8re \u00e0 Beth-Leaphra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.11","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:11","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Passe, habitante de Schaphir, dans la nudit\u00e9 et la honte!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019habitante de Tsaanan n\u2019ose sortir,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le deuil de Beth-Ha\u00ebtsel vous prive de son abri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.12","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:12","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>L\u2019habitante de Maroth tremble pour son salut,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Car le malheur est descendu de la part de l\u2019\u00c9ternel<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la porte de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.13","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:13","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Attelle les coursiers \u00e0 ton char,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Habitante de Lakisch!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 pour la fille de Sion une premi\u00e8re cause de p\u00e9ch\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car en toi se sont trouv\u00e9s les crimes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.14","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:14","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi tu renonceras \u00e0 Mor\u00e9schet-Gath;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Les maisons d\u2019Aczib seront une source trompeuse<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour les rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.15","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.15","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:15","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.001.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Je t\u2019am\u00e8nerai un nouveau ma\u00eetre, habitante de Mar\u00e9scha;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">La gloire d\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019en ira jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Adullam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.16","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.16","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 1:16","prev_osis_id":"Mic.001.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.1.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Rase-toi, coupe ta chevelure,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A cause de tes enfants ch\u00e9ris!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Rends-toi chauve comme l\u2019aigle,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car ils s\u2019en vont en captivit\u00e9 loin de toi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.2.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.1.15","name":"Mich\u00e9e 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.1.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49